item.description: Seacoast Spanish speakers of all ages, levels are welcome! Let's meet to practice Spanish and pasarlo bien con un cafecito (have a good time over some coffee)! Our first meeting is Sunday, Sept. 3 at Cafe on the Corner in Dover, NH at 4:00 pm. Following meetings to alternate between Dover and Portsmouth. Please come!
